@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_silvvy(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.cos(v0)
    v0 = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.19) - 0.05) / (0.77 * wp.cos(v2 + 0.41)))
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v1 + 0.24)) * v2)
    tmp = 0.61
    v2 = 0.47
    tmp = v1
    v2 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.65) + v2) / (0.13 * wp.exp(v2 + 0.34)))
    data[tid] = v0
